modules.description: This module creates and manages animated numeric displays using a configured HTML element. It initializes an odometer with options like value, formatting, theme, and animation, and allows updating the displayed value dynamically. Concrete use cases include real-time data dashboards and interactive UI components where numerical values change smoothly.
